        u: "<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　<br /> </span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí<br /> </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>For 30 minutes,</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> the target's Defense is increased by </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>.<br /> This effect does not stack with </span><span style='color:#ffff11'>Charity's Salvation</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>.<br /> Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>10</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây. Range: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%.1f</span><span style='color:#ffffff;'> yards.</span>",
